Rudy Gobert iced the game with two free throws.
Nikola Jokic had a chance to tie the game at 119, but Gobert forced an errant corner 3-pointer with 2.3 seconds to go.
Gordon led the Nuggets with 31 points and 11 rebounds.
Michael Porter Jr. added 26 points for the Nuggets.
Jamal Murray was lost to the concussion protocol in the third quarter after colliding with Julius Randle.
Braun dunked over Rudy Gobert with 5:14 left and taunted him, leading to a technical foul for both players.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Timberwolves, who led the league in defense last season, allowed 22 fast-break points.
